title: Testimony ends in trial over Jay Z's rap hit 'Big Pimpin"
text: > Entertainment Testimony ends in trial over Jay Z's rap hit 'Big Pimpin" FILE - In this April 16, 2014 file photo, Shawn "Jay Z" Carter announces the Made in America Festival from the steps of City Hall in Los Angeles. Testimony in a copyright infringement trial filed by the heir of an Egyptian composer against Jay Z over his 1999 hit "Big Pimpin'" concluded in Los Angeles on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015. (Photo by Paul A. Hebert/Invision/AP, File)
